{{STFeature}}

int '''GetInvasionWave''' (void)

==Usage==

Returns the current wave of a Skulltag invasion game, however if Invasion is not running then expect a value of <code>-1</code> to be returned instead.

==Example==

 Script 1 OPEN
 {
 While((GetInvasionWave() != 2))
  {
  Delay(1);
  }
  Print(s:"The second wave started!");
 }
